---

# 5. Screen Designs

## 5.1 Home Screen

### Purpose

Entry point for user action

### Layout

* Title: ScanStruct
* Subtitle: “Turn any document into structured data”
* Buttons:

  * Take Photo
  * Upload Image

---

## 5.2 Preview Screen

### Purpose

Confirm selected image

### Layout

* Image preview
* Buttons:

  * Retake
  * Extract Data

---

## 5.3 Processing Screen

### Purpose

Show system working state

### Layout

* Loader
* Text:

  * “Extracting text…”
  * “Understanding document…”

---

## 5.4 Review Screen (Core)

### Purpose

Allow user to verify and edit AI-generated structured data

### Layout

Top:

* Image thumbnail

Below:

* Document Type (auto-detected)

Dynamic Fields Section:

[ Key ] [ Value ]
[ Name ] [ Abhishek Kumar Singh ]
[ Department ] [ Income Tax Department ]

Actions:

* Add Field
* Delete Field

Optional:

* Show Raw Text toggle

Bottom:

* Export Format Selector:

  * JSON
  * CSV
  * TXT

* Export Data button

---

## 5.5 Export Screen

### Purpose

Confirm export and allow sharing

### Layout

* Success icon
* Text: “Data ready”

Buttons:

* Download
* Share
* Scan Another

---

# 6. Interaction Design

## 6.1 Dynamic Field Behavior

* Edit keys
* Edit values
* Add fields
* Delete fields

## 6.2 AI Transparency

* Show: “AI extracted this data. Please review.”

## 6.3 Loading Feedback

* OCR stage
* AI stage

---

# 7. Edge Cases

## 7.1 AI Extraction Failure

Show message and allow manual entry

## 7.2 No Structured Fields

Allow user to add fields manually

## 7.3 Poor OCR

Show raw text and allow reconstruction

## 7.4 Unknown Document

Set type as “Unknown”

---

# 8. Accessibility

* Buttons ≥ 48px
* Readable text
* High contrast

---

# 9. Performance Guidelines

* Target < 5 seconds
* Progressive feedback

---

# 10. Do’s and Don’ts

## Do

* Keep UI flexible
* Allow user control

## Don’t

* Hardcode fields
* Overpromise AI

---

# 11. Definition of Design Done

* Dynamic fields working
* Editable AI output
* Export works
* UI supports any document type

---

# Final Note

This is a universal document-to-structured-data interface powered by AI.

Success = user can convert any document into usable structured data quickly.
